From 70ae244c7e5aacf5804f9ed3990ee5c26533c983 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Drew Noakes <git@drewnoakes.com>
Date: Sun, 3 Apr 2022 22:04:05 +1000
Subject: [PATCH] Refactor MP4 handling

Fixes several issues flagged by drewnoakes/metadata-extractor#561

This change removes the object hierarchy for boxes, making the processing of data more linear, allocating less memory, and making it clearer where we are not using the values we read.
